                        description "0x8848/MPLS multicast/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 733 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8863/PPPoE Discovery/PADI/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                            etype 0x8863
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 766 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8863/PPPoE Discovery/----/Multicast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac 01:00:5e:00:00:00 ff:ff:ff:80:00:00
                            etype 0x8863
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 799 create
                        action accept

                            etype 0x8863

                    exit

                exit

                dscp cs3 fc l2 profile in
                dscp cs4 fc h1 profile in
                dscp cs5 fc af profile in

                lsp-exp 2 fc l2 profile in
                lsp-exp 3 fc l2 profile in
                lsp-exp 4 fc h1 profile in
                lsp-exp 5 fc af profile in
                lsp-exp 6 fc nc profile in
                lsp-exp 7 fc af profile in
            exit
            egress
                remarking
                fc af
                    dscp-in-profile cs5
                    dscp-out-profile cs5
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 5
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 5
                exit
                fc h1
                    dscp-in-profile cs4
                    dscp-out-profile cs4
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 4
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 4
                exit
                fc nc

echo "Mirror Configuration"
#--------------------------------------------------
    mirror 
        mirror-dest 2 create
            shutdown
        exit 
        mirror-dest 444 create
            sap 6/2/2 create 
            exit 
            slice-size 1400 
            no shutdown
        exit 
        mirror-dest 1000 create
            shutdown

                egress
                    vc-label 3333
                exit
                no shutdown
            exit
        exit 
        mirror-dest 1001 type ppp create
            shutdown

                egress
                    vc-label 4444
                exit

            exit
        exit 
        mirror-dest 2000 create

            exit
        exit 
    exit
